Nostalgia Network Inc said it signed anagreement with the ACTS Satellite Network to produce a seriesof two- and five-minute commercials of its home shoppingservice, "Collectible Showcase."    It said the ACTS Network, with more than six mln cabletelevision subscribers, will air the commercials approximately28 times a week for 13 weeks, and as a result NostalgiaNetowork said it expects a significant increase in sales volumein April.    Nostalgia is 29 pct owned by Futuresat Industries Inc. Reuter&#3;